  "title": "Admin Executive",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Support the corporate secretarial Business Unit for compliance and admin work</li><li>Lodgment of documents with ACRA/ MOM and other governmental authorities and/or\n     departments related to corporate services work.</li><li>To track and monitor deadlines and requirements to ensure adherence to statutory and regulatory obligations.</li><li>Assist in KYC/due diligence procedures in accordance with internal policies.</li><li>Perform any other additional responsibilities and/ or ad-hoc duties as assigned by the various head(s) of departments from time to time.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Minimum 3 years of working experience in the related field; </li><li>Diploma or higher qualification in Business, Law, or a related discipline; </li><li>Proficiency in Mandarin as liaison with clients from Mainland China is required; </li><li>Familiarity with the Singapore Companies Act and corporate compliance requirements will be a plus; </li><li>Good verbal and written communication skills in English and Mandarin to effectively communicate with Mandarin-speaking clients;</li><li>Able to work independently as well as a Team; </li><li>Meticulous, well-organised and good interpersonal skill with positive attitude; </li><li>Able to meet tight deadlines in fast-paced work environment. </li></ul>",
